Cryptis database website

!!BUILD
mvn spring-boot:run - run server locally
mvn clean package - create executable jar
docker build -f src/main/docker/Dockerfile /target/

Контейнер зависит от базы данных
SPRING_DATASOURCE_PASSWORD - пароль к контейнеру с СУБД postgres
SHELL_AUTH_SIMPLE_USER_PASSWORD - пароль к ssh сессиии


Пример compose
cat docker-compose.yml
cryptis-web:
  image: ru.cryptis.web
  links:
    - postgresdb-db:postgres
  ports:
    - "127.0.0.1:your-port-here:80"
  environment:
    SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE: production
    SPRING_DATASOURCE_PASSWORD: your-password-here
    SHELL_AUTH_PASSWORD: your-password-here
